articles.title: Phase 3 trial of new malaria vaccine reveals promising results in protecting children - News-Medical.Net
articles.description: Today, peer-reviewed results from a Phase 3 efficacy trial of the R21/Matrix-M™ malaria vaccine were published in The Lancet. The study was conducted across multiple sites in four African countries with 4,800 children aged 5-36 months.
